      • getCrawlInfoPath

        public static String getCrawlInfoPath(UUID uuid,
                      @Nullable
                      String path)
        Helper method to retrieve a path under the CRAWL_INFO node.
        Parameters:
        uuid - of the dataset to get the path for
        path - if null we retrieve the path of the CRAWL_INFO node itself otherwise we append this path
